You can directly add the reactions in the queue callback:

```java
event.getChannel().sendMessage(&quot;This is a message&quot;).queue(message -&gt; {
        message.addReaction(&quot;U+1F1E6&quot;).queue();
        message.addReaction(&quot;U+1F1E7&quot;).queue();
